land.headline: INSTRUCTIONS TO SELL
land.description:
Don't delay in securing this wonderful parcel of land that provides you the perfect opportunity to build with your own builder to ensure that your dream home is everything that you hoped it would be.
With multiple parks, recreation spots and multiple children's playgrounds, this estate is ideal for outdoor living. This is situated next to the exclusive Denham Court and conveniently close to local schools, Edmondson Park Railway Station, local shopping facilities, the M5 and M7 motorways.
Features:
•Approx. 250 sqm block of land •Frontage: 10m approx. •Depth: 25m approx.
Edmondson Park is fast becoming a community with modern amenities and a fantastic family-friendly lifestyle. If you want to be a part of this up and coming area and enjoy the benefits of ideal location, then please make sure you submit offer before it is sold. Please contact your exclusive agent Jitender Singh on 0410 567 777 and Atul Bhanushali on 0402 961 515.
